  m_Name: Gacha games
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::IconsSO
  iconImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d19a97640e6f558409a84f34f5bf4a4f, type: 3}
  description: "Gacha games are typically free-to-play games that have a gachapon
    mechanism. Gachapon are a type of vending machine that randomly spits out a prize
    after putting money into it. Gacha games are extremely popular in China.\r\n\r\nThere
    are many gacha games in the Chinese market at the moment. The most famous of
    which are games from Mihoyo (Genshin Impact, Honkai Star Rail), Hypergryph (Arknights),
    Kuro games (Wuthering Waves) and Paperfold games (Infinity Nikke, Love and Deep
    Space). In most of these games, male characters tend to be portrayed as slender,
    effeminate looking characters. \r\n"
